                        <p>以夸张的手臂动作和表演性为特色，源自70年代迪斯科文化的舞蹈风格</p>
                        <a href="#" class="category-btn">了解更多</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="category-card">
                    <div class="category-image">
                        <img src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=krumping%20dancer%20with%20intense%20facial%20expression%2C%20aggressive%20movements%2C%20urban%20background&image_size=square" alt="Krumping">
                    </div>
                    <div class="category-content">
                        <h3>Krumping</h3>
                        <p>以强烈的表现力和情感释放为特色，充满力量和速度的舞蹈风格</p>
                        <a href="#" class="category-btn">了解更多</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- 最新活动/课程展示模块 -->
    <section class="events" id="events">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>最新活动</h2>
